    <article id="en" class="card" lang="en" style="display:none">
      <p class="muted">Effective: 08 Nov 2025</p>
      <h2 id="p1-en">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p><strong>1. Controller</strong> – <em>[NAME / COMPANY], [STREET + NO], [ZIP CITY], Germany, [EMAIL]</em></p>
      <p><strong>2. Overview</strong> – Works without account; data stored <strong>locally</strong>; no server transfer or tracking; subscription flag stored locally.</p>
      <p><strong>3. Categories of Data</strong> – Usage data (goals, daily values, tasks, XP/level, streaks, achievements); subscription flags; optional notifications; sensors inactive.</p>
      <p><strong>4. Purposes &amp; Legal Bases</strong> – Art. 6(1)(b) (functionality); Art. 6(1)(a) (consent e.g. notifications); Art. 6(1)(f) (security/bug fixing locally).</p>
      <p><strong>5. Storage / Retention</strong> – Local until uninstall/reset.</p>
      <p><strong>6. Recipients / Third Countries</strong> – None; if services added later, we’ll inform and obtain consent where required.</p>
      <p><strong>7. Data Subject Rights</strong> – Access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability, objection; withdraw consent anytime.</p>
      <p><strong>8. Minors</strong> – Not for children under 16.</p>
      <p><strong>9. Security</strong> – Local storage; protect your device.</p>
      <p><strong>10. Changes</strong> – Updated if features/laws change.</p>
      <p><strong>11. Contact</strong> – <em>[NAME / COMPANY], [STREET + NO], [ZIP CITY], [EMAIL]</em></p>
